Action: Searching for a supplied value within a supplied array
Input: Array to be searched, value to search for
Output: Position of value in array

//VALIDATION

// SETUP:
Create variable to track current start of data and set to 0
Create variable to track current end of data and set to array.length-1

while start <= end:
    Create variable to track mid : start + (end-start)/2
    if data at mid equals value:
        Return mid
    else if data at mid < value:
        Set start to mid+1
    else:
        Set end to mid-1

return -1